<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Nihin Khamhbawi an auh, Lampalh mi ra; Nangmah thlarau a tlau, Palh in
 kal hlah.

[V2]
 Khamhbawi Jesuh a au, Atu ngai tuah; Biaknak inn ah ra tuah, Jesuh
 sinah.

[V3]
 Nihin Jesuh au ko, Dornak kawl tuah; Biaceihnak thli a hrang, Thihnak
 nai ta.

[V4]
 Thiang Thlarau nih an auh, A bia ngai tuah; Lut tuah ngaihchia loin,
 Zaang an fah lai.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<title>NIHIN KHAMHBAWI AN AUH CH221</title>
<hymn_number>221</hymn_number>
</song>